
Ranger Help for: furyfire
=========================

SYNTAX:      furyfire <target>
USAGE:       Any terrain
SLOT COST:   14
BASE SP:     variable
SKILL TYPE:  bow

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to make full use os the easy loading
ability of the shortbow. Several factors go into how well a furyfire
goes, such as dexterity. When a ranger furyfires, he or she lets go
a volley of arrows all in the span of mere seconds. Whatever the Ranger
has set as the shortbow's loader will be used in furyfire. The best
arrows in the loader will automatically be used in the volley. There
must be at least 4 arrows in the loader in order for a Ranger to
furyfire.

